items.description: This booth is still small but bigger

Eye-catching stand with elegant and dramatic “floor-to- ceiling” illuminated tradeshow booth with ‘all that you need’: Inviting bar, 2 separate meeting spaces and storage.
Includes:
  • All Hardware as shown
  • New Graphics with your artwork
  • Lights
  • Counter
  • Single Color carpet
  • Furniture (as per availability)
  • Friendly Expert Project Management
